      "title": "TPA, ACMC, SLMC to back Dullas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Tamil Progressive Alliance (TPA), All Ceylon Makkal Congress (ACMC) and Sri Lanka Muslim Congress (SLMC) decided to back Dullas Alahapperuma in the vote to elect a new President today.",
        "The Tamil Progressive Alliance (TPA) unanimously decided to support Dullas Alahapperuma. Its leader Mano Ganesan MP told the media after the party presidium meeting held at the party secretariat at Nugegoda.",
        "Also, the ACMC and the SLMC decided to back Mr. Alahapperuma. (Yohan Perera)"
      ],
